@startuml
title UML State Chart Diagram (Video Suggestion System)

[*] --> RequestSuggestion


state "Request Suggestion" as RequestSuggestion
RequestSuggestion : entry / Check network connection between server and user 
RequestSuggestion : do / send request signal
RequestSuggestion : exit / Get unique user ID

state "Retrieve Unique Id" as RetrieveID
RetrieveID : entry / Request from a user
RetrieveID : do / Get unique ID of that user
RetrieveID : exit / trigger all suggestion functions

RequestSuggestion --> RetrieveID


state Fork1 <<fork>>
RetrieveID --> Fork1

state "Other Videos watched by similar users" as SimilarUsers
SimilarUsers : entry / Get user ID
SimilarUsers : do / Get similar users watching videos
SimilarUsers : exit / retreive the attributes of videos 
state "Trending Videos" as Trending
Trending : entry / Get user ID
Trending : do / Get trending for the user's localty
Trending : exit / retreive the attributes of videos 
state "Similar Tag Videos" as SimilarTag
SimilarTag : entry / Get user ID
SimilarTag : do / Get similar tag videos
SimilarTag : exit / retreive the attributes of videos 
state "Similar Genre Videos" as SimilarGenre
SimilarGenre : entry / Get user ID
SimilarGenre : do / Get similar videos
SimilarGenre : exit / retreive the attributes of videos 
state "Paid Promotion Videos" as PaidPromo
PaidPromo : entry / Get user ID
PaidPromo : do / Get promotion videos for the user
PaidPromo : exit / retreive the attributes of videos 

Fork1 --> SimilarUsers
Fork1 --> Trending
Fork1 --> SimilarTag
Fork1 --> SimilarGenre
Fork1 --> PaidPromo


state Join1 <<join>>

SimilarUsers --> Join1
Trending --> Join1
SimilarTag --> Join1
SimilarGenre --> Join1
PaidPromo --> Join1


state "Retrieve Other Attributes of videos" as RetrieveAttr
RetrieveAttr : entry / Get video IDs
RetrieveAttr : do / Retrieve thumbnails, views
RetrieveAttr : exit / Suggest video

Join1 --> RetrieveAttr

state "Suggest Videos" as SuggestVideos
SuggestVideos : entry / Get suggestion videos with attributes
SuggestVideos : do / Send videos to the user
SuggestVideos : exit / Ensure sent videos reached

RetrieveAttr --> SuggestVideos

SuggestVideos --> [*]

@enduml